hopobject.body: I'm interested in price manforce tablet "I think having that competition with Nick drove him to be excellent, to chase perfection every chance he got. And it's the same way with Nick. I think just the preparation, when guys manage the attitude and keeping the offense together. And as you can see, I think the last couple of preseason games we had they both played well. But the good thing is, with two starters I would say - knowing that Mike's the starter - but if anything ever happens, in this league, you know the biggest thing is depth. I think we have a lot of depth at the quarterback position and all over the offense. I think it's a positive thing that we have two good quarterbacks.
